nt some previously\nunreported TTVs. Finally transit durations help distinguish between false\npositives and true planets and we use our measurements to confirm six new\nexoplanets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 May 2015 21:54:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-08-06"}
