d, while the subleading\nlogarithmic term does not. Finally, the luminosities of black holes are\ncomputed by using the geometric optics approximation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 May 2015 15:03:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 1 Nov 2017 03:24:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-08"}
